#Identificar y manejar datos discrepantes en variables num茅ricas

### Identificaci贸n de outliers de edad

<aside>
 Se utiliza el Z-Score ya que Age tiene una distribuci贸n normal

</aside>

```sql
WITH stats AS (
  SELECT
    AVG(age) AS mean_age,
    STDDEV(age) AS stddev_age
  FROM `erudite-scholar-426802-h9.proyecto3_riesgo.user_info`
  WHERE age IS NOT NULL
),
z_scores AS (
  SELECT
    *,
    (age - (SELECT mean_age FROM stats)) / (SELECT stddev_age FROM stats) AS z_score
  FROM `erudite-scholar-426802-h9.proyecto3_riesgo.user_info`
),
flagged AS (
  SELECT
    *,
    CASE
      WHEN z_score > 2 OR z_score < -2 THEN 'Outlier'
      ELSE 'Within'
    END AS outlier_flag_age
  FROM z_scores
)
SELECT *
FROM flagged
WHERE outlier_flag_age = 'Outlier';

```

